{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001857.wav", "text": "吃现在要排队，吾也第一趟碰着，哪能吃侪要排队唻", "speaker_id": "G0075", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003746.wav", "text": "对伐拧辣活辣搿呃地球高头呢也说伐出有其他呃陪伴呃拧对伐", "speaker_id": "G1378", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003739.wav", "text": "养宠物呢一呃呢要宠物呢也要，对伐总归有规矩", "speaker_id": "G1378", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000413.wav", "text": "阿拉再来旅，聊聊旅游休闲呃事体", "speaker_id": "G0008", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003549.wav", "text": "诶现在贺年卡也伐发了，圣诞节也好撒呃节侪是诶互联网高头发发", "speaker_id": "G1378", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000953.wav", "text": "但是孝敬爷娘，吾觉着没阿拉搿一代孝敬爷娘", "speaker_id": "G0010", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003503.wav", "text": "该哪能样子处理嘛，就搿能样子呃，屋里相教育小拧呃事体嘛，大家侪统一呃侪搿能样子", "speaker_id": "G1349", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000326.wav", "text": "吾到底出伐出来但是，吾吾同事哦，伊账面高头五百万哦", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001185.wav", "text": "葛末等于讲开开胃", "speaker_id": "G0017", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003166.wav", "text": "到伊功课做好弄好了葛末侬再好有的侬呃娱乐生活葛末", "speaker_id": "G1350", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000933.wav", "text": "台子哴就是搿能噶一杯杯物事，小拧伐吃茶了", "speaker_id": "G0009", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002708.wav", "text": "侬搿只高价位", "speaker_id": "G1273", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000187.wav", "text": "因为吾做过财务嘛吾讲侬如果讲，侬开了三四年", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000284.wav", "text": "二趟是，诶，第二趟是二万", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002885.wav", "text": "天天", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000787.wav", "text": "阿拉就跑了搿几呃，乃末伊后头阿拉组织科科长也蛮好，就讲吾了，诶，侬跑几呃地方还蛮好，侪大城市", "speaker_id": "G0010", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002364.wav", "text": "旅游团呃现在伐是[+]", "speaker_id": "G0218", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001481.wav", "text": "米线面馆吾来得呃欢喜吃", "speaker_id": "G0076", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003529.wav", "text": "对伐侪自家呃小拧呢侪有的一间小房子，自家有得小天地了对伐", "speaker_id": "G1377", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003626.wav", "text": "对伐，但是呢带呐吾发现像下一代呢隔代样呃，确实是一呃问题", "speaker_id": "G1378", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002533.wav", "text": "哦，葛末吾搿呃喃还伐是老懂呃，所以吾股票喃呃伐大敢买，买了伐晓得哪能噶操作", "speaker_id": "G1274", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002574.wav", "text": "呃价钿么也比较埃呃辣手，因为对阿拉工程工拧搿呃", "speaker_id": "G1274", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003397.wav", "text": "葛末就讲，互相照应蹲辣一道，还种嘛是到", "speaker_id": "G1349", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001200.wav", "text": "乃末伊呢，阿拉为啥道理讲伊难服侍，伊今朝吃辣搿物事呢，明朝是伐吃呃", "speaker_id": "G0018", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002261.wav", "text": "今年子到现在还没撒做过伊生活，疫情到现在没撒做过", "speaker_id": "G0218", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000322.wav", "text": "还辣辣涨，侪是涨嘛，伊也涨伐了多少，也最多涨一块二块最多了", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001550.wav", "text": "云南搿呃辰光，有的搿呃叫撒榴莲伐啦", "speaker_id": "G0075", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000511.wav", "text": "嗯，当吾来啦，啥物事呃，一讲讲了老吓人呃", "speaker_id": "G0007", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002196.wav", "text": "拔侬听了老伐适宜呃", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001881.wav", "text": "阿拉上来，现在还伐想穿啊", "speaker_id": "G0076", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002988.wav", "text": "葛末后头喃，吾听阿拉朋友讲，伊讲伊拉后头喃情愿也经常到搿班饭店去吃，因为为撒道理去吃了以后喃", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000177.wav", "text": "吾朋友老冲动呃", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003305.wav", "text": "搿关系呢就讲大家侪是讲老巧妙呃，其实上侪老巧妙大家要一道要想好", "speaker_id": "G1349", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001083.wav", "text": "斩成工丝哦，然后拿伊浸辣海，浸一天", "speaker_id": "G0018", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002472.wav", "text": "碰着实际问题侬伐是到正规呃保险公司侬一眼都伐保险，麻烦呃吓拧", "speaker_id": "G1273", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001408.wav", "text": "葛末伊搿是呒没骨头呃，吾就回来拿伊搿能介刀对伐，一片片一片片搿能介切下来", "speaker_id": "G0018", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003471.wav", "text": "所以阿拉现在六个拧精力基本上侪铺辣伊高头", "speaker_id": "G1350", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001470.wav", "text": "吃得来，毛病侪出来唻，现在伐是讲吃呃问题唻，现在要限制吃，阿拉现在看像吃了忒油", "speaker_id": "G0075", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000396.wav", "text": "就人家伐拿呃，好拿呃拿了一部分呃像搿部分钞票呢作为", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001556.wav", "text": "侬埃面有拧啊，难道侬埃面有的撒拧辣辣埃面啊", "speaker_id": "G0075", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000379.wav", "text": "基本上就是讲，侬像侬讲呃温州银行", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000418.wav", "text": "车子伐是要绕来绕去上去对伐，吾就是晕车呃", "speaker_id": "G0007", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001378.wav", "text": "就讲老早呢，吾就讲牙齿好呃辰光呢，就讲是", "speaker_id": "G0018", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003127.wav", "text": "嗯，花头呃或者是一式头呃，下头应该配撒呃裤子配撒呃裙子，阿拉喃就会得搭配好", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000881.wav", "text": "结果后头来伊拉搿呃拧又没看到吾", "speaker_id": "G0010", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000636.wav", "text": "八个十个葛末一部车子包拨那，葛末拿搿饿车子价钿算一算", "speaker_id": "G0008", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001138.wav", "text": "饭店里相到一直吃呃，因为搿道菜对伐是老伤功夫呃晓得伐", "speaker_id": "G0017", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001393.wav", "text": "葛末，嗯，假使考究点嘛鳝背，", "speaker_id": "G0017", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001731.wav", "text": "铁观音伊拉实际上呢，像人家有个保健品伊拉公司里看看伊拉老板吃呃铁观音哪能呢", "speaker_id": "G0076", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002859.wav", "text": "假使讲没拧流量呢，想吃", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000653.wav", "text": "安吉呢还是可以呃，因为伊为啥道理，侪是竹竹林嘛", "speaker_id": "G0008", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003300.wav", "text": "搿吾心里也老感恩哦，搿新妇蛮好上海能够听到搿能噶新妇好，也属于体量大呃", "speaker_id": "G1349", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003108.wav", "text": "侬伐要讲，生活当中交交关关学问哦", "speaker_id": "G1307", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000026.wav", "text": "现在对伐，老早金融行业呢，本身就是伐保本呃，也伐保本呃所谓五十万赔偿呃损失，是侬做是撒", "speaker_id": "G0004", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003560.wav", "text": "阿拉呢就讲好像，现在呢就讲越来越搿能噶样子，觉着呐伐像老早点搿能噶介开心了", "speaker_id": "G1377", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003315.wav", "text": "伐好辣辣儿子面前讲新妇张三讲新妇李四伐好讲", "speaker_id": "G1349", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001139.wav", "text": "哦呦，吾老怕烧呃诶呦辰光长", "speaker_id": "G0017", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002413.wav", "text": "哦，黄陂北路，[+]", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001839.wav", "text": "活呃，酸呃，甜酸苦辣侪有呃，只要侬想吃啊里个地方哴相呃菜，侪有", "speaker_id": "G0076", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000902.wav", "text": "瞌睡没了诶，有两呃老阿姨嘛", "speaker_id": "G0009", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001718.wav", "text": "葛末等于浪费，就讲搿能理解", "speaker_id": "G0075", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002232.wav", "text": "为了为了好心拧，大概伐[+]", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002872.wav", "text": "选择好侬好看得到伊搿排排名啊，伊搿呃就是讲", "speaker_id": "G1307", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002661.wav", "text": "是几百万，人家拆迁卖了多少有的多少多少，侬伐卖特等于零", "speaker_id": "G1273", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002932.wav", "text": "伊车子老撒侪是自家等于是去，诶，也是蹲勒埃面头农家乐", "speaker_id": "G1307", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000814.wav", "text": "阿拉呃搿楼顶高头，有的种噶人家撒撒铁架架", "speaker_id": "G0009", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002298.wav", "text": "像侬假使一般性辣外头，一日到夜辣辣应酬呃", "speaker_id": "G0218", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000108.wav", "text": "搿为撒的提出搿一百万埃呃讲埃呃埃呃线呢，是就是讲，国家已经晓得", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002465.wav", "text": "买了呢搿趟子呢吾也又去买了一份，吾觉着喃保险喃是伊呃，应该讲", "speaker_id": "G1274", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002069.wav", "text": "诶，侬，侬现在一呃号头退休工资现在好拿几钿啊[+]", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000952.wav", "text": "小青年迭侬讲，脑子现在是比阿拉先进了", "speaker_id": "G0010", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000895.wav", "text": "只有女呃到机械厂，倒好呃", "speaker_id": "G0009", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000383.wav", "text": "还只上海银行吾伐晓得侬对上海银行有撒撒呃有撒了解伐", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000122.wav", "text": "但是老早也坏特过呃，更加要警惕性，但是呢，阿拉已经习惯性了", "speaker_id": "G0004", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000130.wav", "text": "各方面呃生产啊，各方面呃经济啊，侪比较低潮呃，所以辣搿种情况下头更伐可能进去呃", "speaker_id": "G0004", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001728.wav", "text": "少而精，搿能噶对侬身体各方面", "speaker_id": "G0076", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002418.wav", "text": "那正好出一百块洋钿", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000356.wav", "text": "比较小呃银行，会的比人家高点，为撒，因为伊", "speaker_id": "G0004", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002233.wav", "text": "好心拧大概跟[PII]好哦", "speaker_id": "G0217", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003654.wav", "text": "最好呃衣裳拨伊穿，最好呃有多少钞票拨伊用对伐", "speaker_id": "G1377", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003033.wav", "text": "呃，吾吾晓得撒地方好呃饭店，阿拉也要交流交流，葛末就还是要到好呃地方去", "speaker_id": "G1307", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002771.wav", "text": "现在交关物事伐敢投资，房产么投资拨侬讲起来蛮好呃，但是钞票高头是实在达伐到要求", "speaker_id": "G1274", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000419.wav", "text": "吾就吐得来一体是噶，吐了一马夹袋辣埃面，哦半马夹袋伐好讲一马", "speaker_id": "G0007", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003016.wav", "text": "转盘去转啊，去搛菜啊，侬就坐辣海好唻，伊会得端了侬边哴向，侬只要吃特就可以了，啊是啊", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000571.wav", "text": "伊拉跟跟的去伊拉吃了也好", "speaker_id": "G0007", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000914.wav", "text": "做管做，尽管阿拉讲呃，但是里相呃物事该讲呃讲，伐讲呃侬伐好到下头去", "speaker_id": "G0010", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001003.wav", "text": "像伊拉现在真呃伐能比", "speaker_id": "G0009", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_001126.wav", "text": "搭牢前头侬拿梅干菜搨煸，煸煸煸煸好了", "speaker_id": "G0018", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_003037.wav", "text": "对啊是搿能噶样子，要想到吃就吃，伐要节约，要对得起自家", "speaker_id": "G1308", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000102.wav", "text": "侬刚刚讲到，是有道理呃", "speaker_id": "G0003", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_000456.wav", "text": "对呃，吾想起来了", "speaker_id": "G0008", "gender": "female", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
{"audio": "data/shanghai_audio/shanghai_002619.wav", "text": "就像那阿哥迭呃厂，一旦拨撒拧，传到人家手高头，人家也要吃亏过几趟，失败过几趟，再能回全情", "speaker_id": "G1273", "gender": "male", "source_dataset": "TingChen-ppmc/Shanghai_Dialect_Conversational_Speech_Corpus"}
